        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4.1.1豆浆类",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            107,
            816,
            232,
            831
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4.1.1.1纯豆浆",
        "bbox": [
            107,
            835,
            247,
            850
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "以大豆和水为原料，经制浆、杀菌等工艺加工而成的液态产品。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            855,
            616,
            870
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4.1.1.2调味豆浆",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            107,
            874,
            266,
            888
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在豆浆中添加了风味物质的液态产品。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            893,
            441,
            908
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "GB/T 22106-2008",
